708
00:49:22,140 --> 00:49:24,660
Jangan sampai ada kesalahan
yang merusak reputasi.

709
00:49:24,660 --> 00:49:26,700
Baik itu reputasi hotel

710
00:49:26,900 --> 00:49:28,580
atau reputasi Koki Ian.

711
00:49:51,940 --> 00:49:54,420
Preem, bantu aku rapikan catatan rapat,

712
00:49:54,660 --> 00:49:56,790
